title: The Wire - Season 5 Complete High Quality
description:
A complete season 5 set(10 episodes) of The Wire.
Contains english subtitles for each episode.
If you want the subtitles turned off, think about it for a minute or so.
If you still haven't figured it out, smack yourself upside the head. Now you are free to ask.

Description (kind of a spoiler, but not really)
Season 5 explores the news media, particularly the Baltimore Sun, and contains a Jayson Blair-like plotline. Marlo moves to gain even more control over the drug trade in Baltimore. McNulty goes off the deep end. Freamon and Pearlman are on Clay Davis, and thanks to the financial mismanagement of Carcetti, the "fixing" of city's PD becomes a back-burner issue.

Oh and in the interest of full disclosure, the video gets choppy in one episode for 2 seconds. I've watched them all, and had no other problems. All tested in my dvd player and work fine. Happy watching everyone.

How great was this show?

Feedback is appreciated.
